{"tid":629553,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人唔識分好感，鍾意同愛？","createTime":"2018-04-14T18:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T20:57:07.000Z","uid":114418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"54c94df13dfb22d4cfab5d3b14758924347ef6ff","tid":629553,"uid":114418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:56:01.000Z","msg":"我成日都分唔清"},{"pid":"9caf53ff129db2354c110e34ff56b3ab94ea3445","tid":629553,"uid":46263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T19:28:35.000Z","msg":"好感同鐘意 我都唔係好分得清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但愛既感覺應該係強烈好多好多 會付出多啲"},{"pid":"0d902dafab35142b9a2809f0dcf1effc5e31e9d6","tid":629553,"uid":175580,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T19:37:06.000Z","msg":"我諗好感大慨係你唔抗拒同佢接觸，但佢未至於影響到你<br />\n鍾意係你會開始願意付出<br />\n愛係就算你知付出無回報 會受傷 你都會繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7a0ec696342608035580de8eda2415a35850a1","tid":629553,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:05:53.000Z","msg":"我好愛一個人，佢溫柔，好聰明，唔會輕易放棄，好善良。<br />\n望住佢真係好有力量，佢就咁企我隔離都覺得好幸福。<br />\n佢既存在＝為我付出緊<br />\n<br />\n我會無條件對佢好<br />\n更加唔想佢受傷害<br />\n佢對我無咩感覺<br />\n我擁有唔到佢 我唔會恨佢 會默默繼續珍惜佢"},{"pid":"7aa8155dc56584b5dd1ca00e3966a1033715bd3a","tid":629553,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:08:19.000Z","msg":"我之前拍緊拖果陣會計計地，我就自己都唔係好愛佢。<br />\n因為當初係一見鐘情，我唔係鐘意佢內在.....<br />\n果陣繼續一齊只係因為我寂寞，佢又對我幾好咁。<br />\n<br />\n呢d叫鐘意only"},{"pid":"247d13fb72b33562ceb164a5c5ed5e35135c04ca","tid":629553,"uid":86988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:14:48.000Z","msg":"我當程度咁分<br />\n好感:自身唔確定係咪鐘意<br />\n鐘意:自身已確定，希望可以發展關係<br />\n愛:戀人之間嘅情感/愛一個人嘅具體化量詞(0~100%)"},{"pid":"9fdaf5067f842412a4bce75770c05a8846cc5770","tid":629553,"uid":114418,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:38:38.000Z","msg":"我唔敢輕易去講我愛你，因為我覺得講左就一定要做到，但係我又唔確定個份係米愛"},{"pid":"c9b36be84ae4e27680cb052bc332318c1d33e21c","tid":629553,"uid":88001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:39:45.000Z","msg":"我諗 <br />\n好感可以男男女女都有 講啫係朋友咁 見到面你會好開心 <br />\n鍾意係你成日都想見到佢 但都有分多與少 如果少嘅話可能呢成日都想見到佢嘅感覺就會好快消失 多啲就會keep得耐啲<br />\n而愛我諗係要經歷經歷過一啲事之後 通常都係啲低潮位出現 令到你覺得有呢個人真係好 無左佢唔得 願意為左犧牲好多野....掛"},{"pid":"c4ca47c5004d2e83eaf127a2ced36192627c4068","tid":629553,"uid":171555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:40:59.000Z","msg":"好感=你對佢有興趣<br />\n鐘意=你掛住佢<br />\n愛=哈利"},{"pid":"968e4417b400ceb46ece351e41b458c8a50a928f","tid":629553,"uid":88001,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c4ca47c5004d2e83eaf127a2ced36192627c4068","tid":629553,"uid":171555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:40:59.000Z","msg":"好感=你對佢有興趣<br />\n鐘意=你掛住佢<br />\n愛=哈利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:42:55.000Z","msg":"好好笑？"},{"pid":"0d25a80c800e10e748977089835705c9cec4120e","tid":629553,"uid":171555,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"968e4417b400ceb46ece351e41b458c8a50a928f","tid":629553,"uid":88001,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c4ca47c5004d2e83eaf127a2ced36192627c4068","tid":629553,"uid":171555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:40:59.000Z","msg":"好感=你對佢有興趣<br />\n鐘意=你掛住佢<br />\n愛=哈利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:42:55.000Z","msg":"好好笑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:44:53.000Z","msg":"的確唔夠你個人好笑既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a919d8f2c1d8686c7c2da940d66e84a310bdf0","tid":629553,"uid":114418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4ca47c5004d2e83eaf127a2ced36192627c4068","tid":629553,"uid":171555,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T20:40:59.000Z","msg":"